data.description: Welcome to PARADISE just 5.6 miles to Siesta Key Beach! Relax in your Key West style bungalow, float in your oversized 8 ft deep POOL, and head to one of the worlds best beaches! NO HOA fees makes for a perfect primary residence, vacation home, or short term rental in desirable Sarasota Florida! This west facing home and front porch create a cozy place to catch the stunning Southwest Florida sunsets. Our favorite features include the fully enclosed yard with vinyl fence, solid wood walnut doors with bronze knobs throughout, plantation shutters, smooth Corian kitchen countertop and sink, and of course the shark and barracuda tile design on the floor of the in-ground gunite pool! Curious for more? Come see for yourself! Just inside, you will be welcomed into the large light and bright, open living and kitchen areas adorned with skylights, recessed lighting, exposed brick, wide plank wood floors and 5 inch baseboards throughout.  Enjoy the view of the  private backyard oasis from the kitchen and oversized tiled Florida room sipping your morning coffee or evening cocktails.  Don't miss these features: 40 gallon hot water heater new in 2022, Culligan whole house water filtration system new in 2019, newer pool pump (roughly 2019), HVAC new in 2017 and serviced in 2022, washer & dryer new in 2017.  Ashton Elementary, New Gate Montessori, and Sarasota Middle School are all in walking distance. Reap the benefits of a short jog or bike ride 1.2 miles to the Ashton Trailhead of the Legacy Trail. A short drive and your toes are in the incomparable Siesta Key sand and you are gazing upon on the turquoise waters of the Gulf of Mexico at beach access 12. Cue the movers this one is priced to sell! Don't miss it!
